the victims as he wants?

73
00:05:46,320 --> 00:05:47,640
Or should I put it as

74
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:50,280
a situation

75
00:05:50,640 --> 00:05:53,600
where a traitor to the nation

76
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:56,200
wants to keep his position
by sacrificing my brothers' blood?

77
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:57,920
Chuyi,

78
00:05:58,440 --> 00:05:59,280
please stop.

79
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:00,760
