is a capital crime.

91
00:06:55,100 --> 00:06:56,700
(In Memory of
the Warriors Died in Luoxia Ridge)

92
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:59,440
You didn't even kneel

93
00:06:59,880 --> 00:07:01,400
to their souls.

94
00:07:01,880 --> 00:07:03,280
Do you have a heart?

95
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:04,120
Kneel!

96
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:16,720
Brothers.

97
00:07:18,220 --> 00:07:20,420
(In Memory of
the Warriors Died in Luoxia Ridge)

98
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,280
