101
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:29,720
Kowtow!

102
00:07:30,720 --> 00:07:31,800
I was confused

103
00:07:31,800 --> 00:07:32,640
and made a mistake.

104
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:34,640
- General, mercy.
- Did I tell you to stop?

105
00:07:35,320 --> 00:07:36,160
Kneel!

106
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:50,440
(Chuyi, you can't die.)

107
00:07:54,920 --> 00:07:55,960
If you kill him,

108
00:07:56,160 --> 00:07:57,460
I'll die in front of you!

109
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:03,640
Yun,

110
00:08:04,280 --> 00:08:06,080
I know you want to save me.

111
00:08:09,280 --> 00:08:10,160
If one of us has to die,

112
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,160
it has to be me.

113
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:23,200
Watch out!

114
00:08:33,160 --> 00:08:34,000
Yun!

115
00:08:34,040 --> 00:08:34,880
Yunxi!

116
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:36,680
Do you think I'm an idiot?

117
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:39,150
Tear Xiao Chuyi into pieces!

118
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:40,360
Aye!

119
00:08:41,840 --> 00:08:42,680
Arrows!

120
00:08:55,040 --> 00:08:55,880
Run!

121
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:03,080
Lu Yunxi, you really want to kill me.

122
00:09:03,360 --> 00:09:04,600
General, we're here.

123
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:07,200
Who sent you?

124
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:09,360
We swore to fight and die with you.

125
00:09:11,000 --> 00:09:11,840
Take her away.

126
00:09:12,880 --> 00:09:13,960
Leave me here.

127
00:09:14,080 --> 00:09:15,160
Take the prince and leave.

128
00:09:15,230 --> 00:09:16,070
I have a plan.

129
00:09:16,420 --> 00:09:17,850
How can I leave you?

130
00:09:18,260 --> 00:09:19,120
Let's enter the temple.

131
00:09:19,640 --> 00:09:20,560
Let's go.

132
00:09:24,640 --> 00:09:25,480
Xu Da.

133
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,320
Guard the surrounding areas.

134
00:09:27,320 --> 00:09:28,320
Find a place to lock and

135
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,160
keep an eye on him.

136
00:09:39,730 --> 00:09:41,250
Amitabha.

137
00:09:41,270 --> 00:09:42,110
Abbot, sorry for this.

138
00:09:42,560 --> 00:09:44,180
General, no apologies.

139
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:45,240
If I can survive,

140
00:09:45,870 --> 00:09:47,280
I'll definitely repay you.

141
00:09:47,860 --> 00:09:49,840
