148
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:09,680
- Break in!
- Aye!

149
00:10:11,760 --> 00:10:13,560
(The city is shut down.)

150
00:10:14,040 --> 00:10:15,120
(I'll be the one)

151
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:17,280
(who writes the story.)

152
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:20,360
(I hope you'll all die here,)

153
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:22,360
(as long as Yunxi is safe.)

154
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:38,800
Only I can unlock this.

155
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,520
If you use force,

156
00:10:42,680 --> 00:10:43,960
the liquid inside

157
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:45,860
will melt the pills.

158
00:10:46,040 --> 00:10:46,920
Xiao Chuyi,

159
00:10:47,360 --> 00:10:48,590
why don't you kill me

160
00:10:48,920 --> 00:10:50,410
and get the cure?

161
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,280
Xiao Chuyi,

162
00:10:53,280 --> 00:10:54,360
do you dare?

163
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:56,240
If you kill me,

164
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:58,720
everyone here and their family
will be eliminated,

165
00:10:59,000 --> 00:11:00,520
including Lu Yunxi.

166
00:11:06,160 --> 00:11:07,000
Let's wait and see.

167
00:11:07,670 --> 00:11:08,730
When we go back,

168
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:10,600
I'll tell my father.

169
00:11:10,980 --> 00:11:12,130
Go to hell!

170
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:15,560
That vicious woman!

171
00:11:15,880 --> 00:11:17,240
I'll torture her to death!

172
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:20,930
How dare you do this to me?

173
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,440
Xiao Chuyi!

174
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:29,680
General,

175
00:11:30,320 --> 00:11:31,760
