176
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:33,160
We can only guard it for one day.

177
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,520
Any mint leaf?

178
00:11:44,800 --> 00:11:45,640
Find a way

179
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:47,440
