243
00:15:53,340 --> 00:15:55,160
I can not only cure Che

244
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:59,480
but also avenge the brothers
died in Luoxia Ridge.

245
00:16:02,160 --> 00:16:03,320
Any mint leaf?

246
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:16,410
General! General!

247
00:16:32,820 --> 00:16:34,780
♪My cries♪

248
00:16:34,900 --> 00:16:36,500
